            <title>[LU-19459] Kernel 6.17 support</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19459</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Linux commit v6.16-rc1-1-gc6603b1d6556&lt;br/&gt;
block: rename tuple_size field in blk_integrity to metadata_size&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Linux commit v6.16-rc1-8-gca115d7e7546&lt;br/&gt;
tree-wide: s/struct fileattr/struct file_kattr/g&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Linux commit v6.16-rc1-12-g691fb82ca6cc&lt;br/&gt;
make d_set_d_op() static&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Linux commit v6.16-rc1-16-g0b136e7d18fa&lt;br/&gt;
kill simple_dentry_operations&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Linux commit v6.16-rc1-20-ge9d8e2bf2320&lt;br/&gt;
fs: change write_begin/write_end interface to take struct kiocb *&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Linux commit v6.16-rc1-39-ga683a5b2ba23&lt;br/&gt;
fold fs_struct-&amp;gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;lock,seq&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; into a seqlock&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Linux commit v6.16-rc5-68-g234dda7a49ff&lt;br/&gt;
mm: remove zero_user()&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Linux commit v6.16-rc6-1571-g93893a57efd4&lt;br/&gt;
net: s/dev_get_flags/netif_get_flags/&lt;/p&gt;</description>
